{"tid":1863922,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來行政會議啲人未死哂嘅","createTime":"2020-02-05T10:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T12:56:52.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"114b44bc2f2f3e54265f74ac397b342e5971ffc0","tid":1863922,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:58:39.000Z","msg":"行政會議支持政府控疫措施<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代行政會議秘書處發出：<br />\n<br />\n  政府宣布進一步的控疫措施，從內地入境的人士，包括香港居民、內地居民和其他旅客，都需要強制接受檢疫14天。行政會議支持政府作出果斷的措施。政府自從減少跨境口岸的運作後，內地和外國到香港的旅客已經大幅減少，但仍然有不少香港居民進出內地。新措施應該會進一步減少進出內地的人流，以減低病毒傳播的風險。我們希望受影響的香港市民諒解，同心合力應對疫情。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年2月5日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間18時47分<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170623/photo/0623-00176-040b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170623%2Fphoto%2F0623-00176-040b1.jpg&h=986ce3b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n純睇CC台以為咩都要區議員做哂添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d847822e27c7f678d1257af4c12fa3c0c5247099","tid":1863922,"uid":293783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:03:13.000Z","msg":"頭8個太廢"},{"pid":"7665d940c7b598e97fef36c1a46dcbc64fee5ea3","tid":1863922,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d847822e27c7f678d1257af4c12fa3c0c5247099","tid":1863922,"uid":293783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:03:13.000Z","msg":"頭8個太廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"b940939886218e5f8a1c6beabb84536beb58a248","tid":1863922,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}